msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/editdictionarydialog/replace\">This input field is only available if you are editing an exception dictionary or a language-dependent custom dictionary. In exception dictionaries, the field shows the alternative suggestion for the current word in the \"Word\" text box. In language-dependent custom dictionaries, the field contains a known root word, as a model of affixation of the new word or its usage in compound words. For example, in a German custom dictionary, the new word вҖңLitschiвҖқ (lychee) with the model word вҖңGummiвҖқ (gum) will result recognition of вҖңLitschisвҖқ (lychees), вҖңLitschibaumвҖқ (lychee tree), вҖңLitschifruchtвҖқ (lychee fruit) etc.</ahelp>"
